      "id": "830772850079376",
      "score": 3,
      "review_title": "Decent for a free game but not realistic",
      "review_description": "Before reading: I am not disrespecting the creator of the game in any way, I’m just giving my thoughts on the game. I realize there’s only so much you can do with a free game and I realize the quest restrictions.\n\nThis game isn’t horrible but it’s not great. The deformation is alright, it’s not realistic like at all but it’s pretty decent. The gore is very unrealistic and needs some working on. The blood is also unrealistic along with the organs. Like I said, I realize there’s not much you can do with a game like this, and it only recently came out. I’m sure in the future this game will be way better.",
